Name: CodeWalker
About the game: CodeWalker™ is a developer’s tool that allows users to view Source Code as graphical trees in a color-coded logic hierarchy. It features 2D and 3D graphical interfaces that allow a programmer to quickly understand unfamiliar code, debug, and optimize software. ​ CodeWalker™ can currently understand the following languages. C C++ C# Java Python Python-formatted pseudo code We have more language support on the way!
